Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:46.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0250,,#21 毁灭之路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:05.67,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}人革联 天柱极市警察署
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生体数据对照后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认定为绢江·库斯洛德小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请确认
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐 姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Veda的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:01:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 「天人」计划的主干系统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗 利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科纳家族为了这一刻 已经等了200多年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝 经由Veda 调出击退Trinity的部队影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能把我方的数据…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经屏蔽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下载完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是拟太阳炉搭载型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争正在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:50.15,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}非洲大陆 西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 还没跟拉格纳联系上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没呢 没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国都有了新型机 到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥 我们该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现已通过Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在进入Level 6的掌控作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打发时间 请您看看这些情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 拉格纳·哈维已完成GN-X的配置了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 他的使命也就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:39.50,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}UNION 高轨道空间站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你是Flag Fighter吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都不认识 你新来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是AEU的王牌 巴特里克·戈拉索瓦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈拉索瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 最先遭遇Gundam并一败涂地那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别揭人伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你们UNION的一把手在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡上级大尉不参加本次作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 怯场了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UNION的王牌也没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许诬蔑队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反 反对暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的部下失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是UNION的达利尔·达吉准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是AEU的卡蒂·玛内金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责指挥本次作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教  准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我将全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特里克 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然会有战果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则放弃Flag就毫无意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没脸见队长了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统的构筑情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概完成80%了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除了Veda对Gundam的辅助 机师的负担会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:05:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近变得温和多了 菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好倾向 好倾向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麻烦你们 再加把劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从目前情况看来 确实有人利用了Veda的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在没有Veda的情况下对抗同型机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有Veda的辅助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有Gundam和Miss.皇的战术预报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还不知道 她过去曾犯下的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人都会犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也许犯下过天大的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但Miss.皇正是为了偿还过去 才选择了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用酒抚慰痛苦的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能做到这一点的 也只有人类而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 你知道我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位 皇小姐下令在集装箱内待机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚 我就说一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为现在情势不妙 四架Gundam的合作才更显得重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话该去跟刹那·F·清英说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来  索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片土地上 也有了绽放的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳能发电能让土地和人民都回归这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 一定会变得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你不用再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了 索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 会梦到玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 问题在于 我想放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想着要放弃吗 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 即将到达目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶武GN-X部队 开始对「天人」的设施进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再度品尝胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被预测到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击坠一架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了High Mega才击坠一架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被判我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一开始就打算拉我们陪葬吗 拉格纳·哈维
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总 总裁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne 合体解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从敌方部队中央突破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 谢谢你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.60,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}单体操作系统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前E传感器竟然都没有反应 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都换上宇航服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 第一级战斗战备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队 断定为拟太阳炉搭载型19架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19架…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方已捕捉到我方踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我们的专长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam四机从集装箱紧急出动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阵型S34迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队接近至0130
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为能出其不意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集装箱舱门 打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 阵型S34
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.03,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}经济特区 东京
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲 曾是位自由新闻记者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻界里 库斯洛特这个名字无人不知
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐进入本报社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因为父亲的影响吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因受到采访对象公司的诬陷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判刑坐牢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探监的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲经常这样对姐姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探究事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺藤摸瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以绢江如此地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在调查什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她不是交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她 是为了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绢江 她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在进行伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格的专题调查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 伊奥利亚…就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被认为是「天人」创立者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沙慈君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果当时我阻止她的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视认Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测到我们的行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有位优秀的指挥官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相同性能的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟战中不知失败为何物的我更有优势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿透了Field！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的粒子压缩率被解读了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只擦边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先行的两架正接近Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 达利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到我们了 伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回避点 没有回避点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们的毁灭也是计划中的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 Veda的辅助竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统出错 系统出错…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正要接受制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没过瘾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被Veda抛弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的行动很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱吗 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全一样 和当时…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明驾驶着Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法成为Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚厉桑德罗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世界的统一 联合国军的胜利 这是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要留下GN Drive 「天人」组织随时可以东山再起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个欲望很强烈的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球与「天人」 两样都想得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的系统死机 是Veda的介入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照预定方案 变更为我们自己的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了吗 我的 生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了 索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着  还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动起来 Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我动起来啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始运行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 Virtue的系统更换出现错误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 一定要赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人怕出名猪怕壮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我笑纳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校的热吻到手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连本带利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残余的粒子不多了 上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认撤退信号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 上校的热吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这样对不起队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames损伤 Dynames损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂负伤 洛克昂负伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 为了保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同凡响啊 「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然构筑起了备用系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的战术预测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是皇·李·诺列嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机 回收Dynames和Virtue 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉丝汀娜 联系莫雷诺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历桑德罗大人 Level 6完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了 就快…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为临时编成的部队 成果还算过得去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先推进GN Drive的解析和量产化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 我们阵营也能与他们一较高下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的时代结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界将因此而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:55.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ笑顔してた　そんな僕らも　幾年も重ね過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:03.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う景色を　受け入れられずに　もがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:48.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れちゃいけないから Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:22:00.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この広い大地と仲間達のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:55.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}经久不变的笑颜　是这样的我们　在年轮中周而复始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:03.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦身而过的风景　却无法剪下收藏　唯心房中丝缕焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将无谓的自尊远远抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.73,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用温柔将这个世界抱紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使告诉我你的勇气　即使逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.21,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一个人便无法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一日的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.68,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}于我心深处　只步未移
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.59,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:48.38,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为不能忘记 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
